OL,3,CMan who cut down village Christmas
OL,4,Ctree avoids jail sentence
OL,6,FA man who cut down a live Christmas
OL,7,Ftree in a County Durham village, which
OL,8,Fwas also a memorial to those who died
OL,9,Fin world wars, has escaped a jail
OL,10,Fsentence.
OL,12,FDylan McNamara, 26, felled the pine on
OL,13,Fthe village green just hours after
OL,14,Falmost 100 people had watched the
OL,15,FChristmas lights switch-on at Shotton
OL,16,FColliery on 10 December 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
