OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781719875
OL,3,CMan who cut down village Christmas
OL,4,Ctree avoids jail sentence
OL,6,FHe admitted criminal damage at a
OL,7,Fprevious hearing, and at his
OL,8,Fsentencing on Tuesday (16 June),
OL,9,FMcNamara was handed a 10-week jail
OL,10,Fsentence, suspended for 18 months, and
OL,11,Fordered to carry out 200 hours unpaid
OL,12,Fwork by magistrates sitting in Newton
OL,13,FAycliffe.
OL,15,FPaul Doney, prosecuting, said the tree
OL,16,Fhad been in place for 10 years and was
OL,17,Fused as a focal point for the village
OL,18,Fat Christmas, as well as serving as a
OL,19,Fwar memorial.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781719875
OL,3,CMan who cut down village Christmas
OL,4,Ctree avoids jail sentence
OL,6,FHe said the value of the tree was in
OL,7,Fthe thousands of pounds as it had
OL,8,Fgrown to 20ft tall, although the
OL,9,Fprosecution accepted the figure was
OL,10,Fless than #5,000.
OL,12,FStuart Wardle, parish council clerk,
OL,13,Fprovided a statement in which he said:
OL,14,F"I found it disgraceful that someone
OL,15,Fcould do this to the tree.
OL,17,F"It is very well-known locally as a
OL,18,Fwar memorial."
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@AOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
