OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781719875
OL,3,CMan who cut down village Christmas
OL,4,Ctree avoids jail sentence
OL,6,FPolice examined CCTV and identified
OL,7,Fthe defendant, of Bruce Glazier
OL,8,FTerrace, and officers found a saw
OL,9,Fhidden behind the fridge in his
OL,10,Fkitchen.
OL,12,FMcNamara had no previous convictions,
OL,13,Fthe court heard.
OL,15,FAmrit Jandoo, defending, said another
OL,16,Fperson was with McNamara when the tree
OL,17,Fwas felled, but they had not been
OL,18,Fprosecuted.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
