OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781719875
OL,3,CMan who cut down village Christmas
OL,4,Ctree avoids jail sentence
OL,6,FHe said: "This defendant has
OL,7,Fshamefully brought himself into public
OL,8,Fridicule by following another."
OL,10,FMr Jandoo said McNamara had been
OL,11,Fassessed and found to demonstrate
OL,12,Fimpulsivity and a lack of judgment.
OL,14,FHe added: "Clearly, this defendant has
OL,15,Fshown the appropriate remorse and
OL,16,Fwishes to apologise to the court and
OL,17,Fto the public of Shotton Colliery."
OL,19,FMr Jandoo said McNamara had been
OL,20,Fassaulted as a result of his actions.
OL,26,@nD@JOUpD@_O]vD@KOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781719875
OL,3,CMan who cut down village Christmas
OL,4,Ctree avoids jail sentence
OL,6,FThe lawyer said there was no
OL,7,Fexplanation for cutting the tree down,
OL,8,Fother than it was "probably a joke,
OL,9,Fprobably some kind of attention
OL,10,Fseeking", but the defendant himself
OL,11,Fdid not know.
OL,13,FChairman of the Bench William
OL,14,FUnsworth, sentencing, said: "This was
OL,15,Fnot a very nice thing to do, was it,
OL,16,Fespecially when it was a memorial to
OL,17,Fpeople who died in the wars?"
OL,19,FThe magistrates ordered that he must
OL,20,Fpay #520 compensation, which will come
OL,21,Ffrom his benefits.
OL,26,@pD@SOUrD@HO]vD@]OUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
