PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1781719875
OL,3,CMan who cut down village Christmas
OL,4,Ctree avoids jail sentence
OL,6,FMcNamara did not speak to reporters as
OL,7,Fhe left court with his head covered by
OL,8,Fa hood.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/7
